    "geometry": "Reservoir 30 x 14 x 14 um. Light propagates +x (30 um propagation budget, ~56 wavelengths at lam=0.532). Four lateral faces (y_min, y_max, z_min, z_max) each (30 x 14) um, divided into 7x7 = 49 patches per face (so each patch is (30/7 = 4.29) x (14/7 = 2.0) um). 4*49 = 196 patches = 14x14 MNIST pixels. MNIST mapping: image quadrants Q1/Q2/Q3/Q4 (each 7x7) onto faces y_min/y_max/z_min/z_max respectively (locality preserved).",
    "patch_size": "Each patch is 2 x 2 um (14 um / 7 patches). electrode_width_um = 0.5 um = patch pad inside the face.",
